组，今晚试试看」verbatim; all body text and titles verbatim as listed\\nConstraints: must preserve strict 3×3 grid structure with visible gutters or thin borders for clean cutting; all text must be Chinese only, no English, no garbled characters; every cell must be independently readable after cropping; text must be large, legible, and never placed near grid cut lines; overall layout must feel like a publishable new-media editorial graphic\\nAvoid: must avoid cheap marketing feel, excessive decoration, English text, garbled characters, text bleeding across grid lines, content that cannot stand alone after cropping\", \"size\": \"1152x1536\", \"quality\": \"medium\", \"n\": 1, \"output_format\": \"png\"}",
