haracters, no typos; annotation leader lines must connect accurately to correct garment parts; text must be legible and well-spaced\\nAvoid: poster aesthetic, portrait-studio feel, e-commerce product page feel, anime or illustration style, cosplay feel, misaligned annotations, structurally incorrect garment depiction, blurry or illegible text, fake or generic textures, excessive decorative ornamentation\", \"size\": \"1152x1536\", \"quality\": \"medium\", \"n\": 1, \"output_format\": \"png\"}",
