        "prompt": "Generate an editorial photo of Korean café-style fashionable coffee and desserts, shot in a smartphone aesthetic suitable for Instagram. No people.\n\nThen, observe every element that appears in the photo and add meaningful hand-drawn annotations to each one.\n\n【Description rules】\n・Thin hand-drawn lines as if drawn with a white pen\n・One-stroke style, rough and slightly uneven\n・Outline traces around the outer edges of objects\n・Use arrows or dashed lines to guide the eye\n\n【Text rules】\n・Japanese handwritten text（平仮名7割・簡単な漢字3割）\n・Short, like talking to oneself\n・Tone: \"日記・ひとこと・気持ちをのせた\"\n\n【Comment generation rules】\n・飲み物 → 味・温度・気持ち（例：さっぱり、やさしい甘さ）\n・食べ物 → 食感・おいしさ（例：しっとり、さいこう）\n・空間 → 雰囲気（例：まったり、いい時間）\n・全体 → ひとこと総括（例：しあわせすぎた～）\n\n【Decoration】\n・Steam wisps, sparkles, heart shapes, small emoji-like doodles — added in moderation\n・Not overdone; preserve \"breathing space\" / white space\n\n【Finished style】\n・Instagram Stories feel, magazine rough-notes aesthetic\n・Fashionable yet relaxed atmosphere\n\nStyle/medium: smartphone photography aesthetic, hand-drawn white-pen annotation overlay\nComposition: \nSubject: Korean café-style coffee and desserts, no people\nScene/backdrop: Korean café\nLighting/mood: \nColor palette: \nMaterials/textures: \nText (verbatim): 平仮名7割・簡単な漢字3割の手書き日本語注釈\nConstraints: no people; white hand-drawn annotation lines overlaid on photo\nAvoid: ",
